    <h1>Michigan General Liability Insurance</h1>
    <p class="lead">General liability is the foundation policy nearly every Michigan business needs — and the one your clients, landlords, and contracts ask for first. It protects you when someone outside your business is injured or their property is damaged, and it pays to defend you even when the claim is groundless.</p>

    <div class="trust-band">
      <span class="trust-band-item"><span class="stars">★★★★★</span> 4.9 on Google</span>
